Cell.Text: Why live out here all by yourself?
[S] I moved here from Helgen after my family was killed. | At the time I couldn't stand to be around anyone. They all felt sorry for me and I didn't want them to. It was my problem, not theirs.
I'm sorry about your family.
<<Shared>> Don't be like them. Don't feel sorry for me.
Who killed your family?
Two Imperial drunks who thought they were above the law.
Want me to take care of them?
Already did. Part of the reason I'm living out here now. Thanks for offering though.
If you need a bow, there's one on the rack to the left of the door.
I'd give you a bow, but it looks like you've already taken it from the rack.
What are those targets for?
I set up those targets a long time ago. I shoot at them from time to time. Don't want to get rusty with my bow.
Are you any good with your bow?
That I am. You know how to use one?
No, not really.
[S] <<Shared>> Well, let me know if you ever want to practice.
Probably better than you.
[S] <<Shared>> Well, let me know if you ever want to practice.
Let's just say Hircine would be jealous.
[S] <<Shared>> Well, let me know if you ever want to practice.
